collectionMetadata.name: Rentals of Non-Landed Residential Buildings, Quarterly
collectionMetadata.description:
This listing contains summary statistics (median, 25th percentile, 75th percentile and number of rental contracts) of major non-landed private residential projects with at least 10 rental contracts signed in a quarter. 

A major project is defined as one with at least 100 residential units.
